casebody.data:
Leo E. STRINE, Jr., et al., petitioners,
v.
DELAWARE COALITION FOR OPEN GOVERNMENT, INC. No. 13-869. Supreme Court of the United States March 24, 2014.

Motion of TechNet for leave to file a brief as amicus curiae granted. Motion of Law Firms for leave to file a brief as amici curiae granted. Petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Third Circuit denied.
